{
  "texts": [
    "CPT-Only corresponds to the original BASE LLM that has undergone the continual pretraining (CPT) but without any vocabulary adaptation.",
    "It serves as a strong baseline when comparing against vocabulary-adapted models.",
    "We provide basic details of implementation in terms of its LoRA implementation, pretraining corpus and training hyperparameters.",
    "Continual Pretraining using LoRA.",
    "We use one A100 40 GB GPU to carry out the pretraining."
  ]
}